# TDD Workflow

- Default to TDD: test first, implementation second, refactor third.
- For each behavior change, add or update at least one automated test.
- Keep tests readable: arrange, act, assert with clear intent.
- Prefer deterministic tests (no flaky timers/network dependencies).
- If tests cannot be added immediately, document why and add a follow-up task.
